{"tid":2455298,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"金管局：近期資金流走因新股集資後調到中國發展  與政局無關","createTime":"2021-03-21T04:09:27.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-22T00:29:03.000Z","uid":21470,"like":3,"dislike":19,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"208f7c39aea8b68ba1ae0d81dc961a75884307d0","tid":2455298,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T04:09:27.000Z","msg":"余偉文：資金流走因新股活動 與政局無關<br />\n<br />\n金管局總裁余偉文在本台節目表示，近期港匯稍為轉弱，出現資金流走，主要因為早前有內地新股IPO，在港上市集資後，將資金兌換到內地發展，強調與中央修改本港選舉制度並無關係,。<br />\n<br />\n他又表示，過去一、兩年，本港雖然發生好多事，經歷多事之秋，但對本港國際金融中心地位，仍然有信心，指過去向跨國金融機構了解，對方仍然覺得本港金融環境穩定，感到滿意，加上本港司法獨立、普通法等制度維持不變，資本市場包括股票等的增長快。<br />\n<br />\n余偉文又指，不同意美國制裁本港官員，強調本港金融機構沒有受制裁影響，香港金融系統能夠自強，金管局亦會居安思危，做好預案。<br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/local/2383909\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Flocal%2F2383909&d=naoD8C4w5OVxKX0KwUpsfXJTAtm2oKGHsrawk8oVPbs%3D&h=40a6e503\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/local/2383909</a>"},{"pid":"d8b606d8596cb3ad0a2fd5974664ceeae022f17a","tid":2455298,"uid":214502,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T04:10:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />哦"},{"pid":"3a4265f926d7bb6f32cc7caf3cd8d75c4a609415","tid":2455298,"uid":125168,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T04:10:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://media.allauthor.com/images/quotes/img/otto-von-bismarck-quote-never-believe-anything-in-politics.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.allauthor.com%2Fimages%2Fquotes%2Fimg%2Fotto-von-bismarck-quote-never-believe-anything-in-politics.jpg&h=6683e608&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8e73323ca649fdc34c7836b542a4c77883d1fcfd","tid":2455298,"uid":44513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T04:11:14.000Z","msg":"哦。"},{"pid":"70d783ba072f71e6d2ba063758a2329451d0788b","tid":2455298,"uid":54975,"like":0,"d